we were friends or something!

00:21:20.347 --> 00:21:24.251
I mean... good riddance
to that clay doll, right?

00:21:24.284 --> 00:21:26.153
Hey, wait! How dare you--!

00:21:31.658 --> 00:21:33.093
He was...

00:21:33.126 --> 00:21:35.662
